# About Me
### ** Hi All, I’m Pooja Sukhdeve Computer Science Graduate Student . Software Developer · Data Analyst · Web Developer** I’m a Computer Science graduate student at Boston University who loves building clean, scalable, and user-focused software. From cloud-powered applications to full-stack web tools, I enjoy turning complex ideas into fast, functional, and elegant solutions. I work across Python, JavaScript, AWS, and modern frameworks to create systems that are reliable, intuitive, and built with purpose. Above all, I’m passionate about writing code that solves real problems and delivers great experiences for real users.

Software & Web Development

- API integration




Application Development
